high_descs: Head rotate and turn right to the coffeetable.
Pick the bowl from the table.
Head rotate and turn left to the fridge.
Turn right and place the bowl inside the fridge.
Pick the bowl and walk towards the coffeetable.
Place the bowl on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the glass bowl on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffeetable.
Take the bowl from the table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the bowl into the refrigerator and cooled it.
Then take it out and go near the coffeetable.
Put the bowl on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Cooled and placed the bowl on the CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Turn right. Approach the refrigerator. Turn right. keep going, when you reach the second piece of furniture, move right and then left. Reach the coffeetable.
Turn around. At the end of the sofas, turn left. Then turn right and go to the fridge. Stand in front of it.
Open the shelf door. Place the bowl on the left side. Close the doors. Wait 8 seconds. Open the door. Take out the bowl. Close the door.
Turn right, at the end of the shelf, turn left. Move a little and then to the right. Go forward to the coffeetable. Stand in front of it.
Place the bowl on the right side at the far edge of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Find a bowl. Place it first on a shelf and then on a CoffeeTable.
